name: WordMeaningQuiz(Over300+questions)
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: word meaning quiz
des:
Is your word game strong? Do you know the meaning of every word? Come take a quiz and test your word power. 

This quiz asks you 50 question, each question is of 100 points, let's see if you can score those 5000 points.

This skill has over 300+ question, so every next time you play the game the question will be different, which will help you improve yourself, like taking a test.

Do drop a review about the skill, and tell us what you want to see more in the skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
